    <item>
      <title>交易员将焦点转向明年的美国利率前景，黄金价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/gold-holds-four-day-climb-as-us-data-reinforce-rate-cut-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者不再关注下周美国降息的可能性，而是关注未来一年更加不确定的前景，黄金价格结束了连续四天的上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/gold-holds-four-day-climb-as-us-data-reinforce-rate-cut-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 00:27:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Syrah 宣布其莫桑比克石墨矿遭遇不可抗力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/syrah-declares-force-majeure-for-its-graphite-mine-in-mozambique</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于持续的国内动乱，澳大利亚矿业公司 Syrah Resources Ltd. 宣布其位于莫桑比克的 Balama 石墨矿遭遇不可抗力，从而导致其无法偿还美国政府支持的贷款，此后该公司股价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/syrah-declares-force-majeure-for-its-graphite-mine-in-mozambique</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 23:56:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受美国制裁谈判和国际能源署前景关注，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-12</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在连续三天上涨后企稳，因交易员消化了美国可能对俄罗斯和伊朗出口实施更严格限制的评论，并期待国际能源署的月度展望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-12</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 23:31:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国通胀支持美联储降息，亚洲股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国通胀数据温和、支撑美联储本月降息预期的推动下，美国股市结束了连续两天的下跌，亚洲股市周四上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 22:37:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
